statement.value:
CREATE DEFINER="root"@"%" VIEW `metadata_index_view`
WITH (
  SCHEMA_BINDING=OFF
) AS
SELECT
  `metadata_index`.`id` AS `id`,
  `metadata_index`.`urn` AS `urn`,
  `metadata_index`.`path` AS `path`,
  `metadata_index`.`doubleVal` AS `doubleVal`
FROM `metadata_index` AS `metadata_index`
